# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Root .gitignore — medication-reminder (ASP.NET Core + Angular)
# Protects secrets and build artifacts regardless of subtree.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# === Secrets / credentials (NEVER commit) ===
**/appsettings.secrets.json
**/appsettings.Local.json
**/appsettings.Production.json
**/secrets.json
*.pfx
*.p12
*.key
*.pem
.env
.env.*
# NuGet API keys / user secrets
*.nuget.config.local
secrets.*
# Firebase service account credentials (NEVER commit — contains private key)
**/firebase-service-account*.json
**/*-firebase-adminsdk-*.json

# === OS files ===
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# === IDE / editors ===
.idea/
.vs/
.vscode/*
# Claude Code session files (local only, not project code)
.claude/

# === Build outputs (deploy artifacts) ===
# dotnet publish output - deploy only, never committed
deploy/publish-output/
# Angular dist output
angular-client/dist/
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
*.user
*.suo
*.userprefs

# === .NET / ASP.NET build artifacts ===
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/artifacts/
*.dll
*.pdb
*.exe
TestResults/
project.lock.json

# Angular build output merged into backend wwwroot (single-domain deploy).
# Only the hashed/vendored bundle artifacts are ignored; ABP's own
# wwwroot assets (libs/, images/, global-styles.css) stay committed.
**/MedicineReminder.HttpApi.Host/wwwroot/*.js
**/MedicineReminder.HttpApi.Host/wwwroot/*.js.map
**/MedicineReminder.HttpApi.Host/wwwroot/*.css
**/MedicineReminder.HttpApi.Host/wwwroot/*.css.map
**/MedicineReminder.HttpApi.Host/wwwroot/index.html
**/MedicineReminder.HttpApi.Host/wwwroot/favicon.ico
**/MedicineReminder.HttpApi.Host/wwwroot/prerendered-routes.json
**/MedicineReminder.HttpApi.Host/wwwroot/*.txt
!**/MedicineReminder.HttpApi.Host/wwwroot/global-styles.css

# === Angular / Node ===
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.angular/cache
**/tmp/
**/out-tsc/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-error.log
**/coverage/

# === Logs ===
*.log
**/Logs/
